    "S 4The Catholic Times Friday Sept 6 1957 The Washington Letter WASHINGTON With tto adjournment of Congress watch for a shift in emphasis in news paper headlines Once again our attention will be called to a larger picture of the world as it is today We will find it is not a happy one When Congress adjourns or recesses there is usually an ac celeration of Soviet Russian propaganda The Reds appar ently take advantage of the fact that our legislators are out of town and do not have the US Capitol as a powerful sounding board against which to answer Red attacks and detractions Moscows seizure of this hour to announce perfection of the ultimate missile weapon its swaggering even truculent re jection of proposals at the Lon don disarmament conference its arming of Syria its revival of the question of Red Chinas admittance to the United Na tionsthese are but some of the signs that we are in for another siege The September 10 meeting of the General Assembly could Well Read About Ponder I A New Set of Problems Now Making Marriage Click Th tinman heart is roid to be an imperfectly shaped heart It is certainly"
